You wanna be a cheerleader?

379
00:20:17,705 --> 00:20:19,055
Kinda, yeah.

380
00:20:19,207 --> 00:20:20,615
I mean, I don't know,

381
00:20:20,634 --> 00:20:23,209
I wanna dance
and make more friends

382
00:20:23,228 --> 00:20:26,545
