do something different.

383
00:20:26,565 --> 00:20:29,065
Brain-dead definitely counts
as different.

384
00:20:29,142 --> 00:20:30,959
(Hannah)
Come on, the only reason
people like Amber

385
00:20:30,977 --> 00:20:32,605
