with me or anything.

394
00:20:52,999 --> 00:20:54,424
Seriously?

395
00:20:58,321 --> 00:20:59,912
Careful.

396
00:20:59,932 --> 00:21:01,990
(Hannah)
Okay.

397
00:21:02,008 --> 00:21:03,152
